## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

ECS Service Broker for PCF has the following requirements:

+ An external Dell EMC Elastic Cloud Storage system

+ For high-availability and best performance, a load-balancer should also be used

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

* The ECS service broker currently supports a single default namespace and ECS
replication group. If multiple are desired, it's possible to deploy multiple
service brokers.

* Currently, only S3, and NFS protocols are supported through
the broker bindings.

